article.description: — Justin Roberts had 21 points as Georgia State narrowly defeated Georgia Southern 79-75 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Roberts lifts Georgia St. past Georgia Southern 79-75
article.linkText: Roberts lifts Georgia St. past Georgia Southern 79-75
article.story: ATLANTA -- — Justin Roberts had 21 points as Georgia State narrowly defeated Georgia Southern 79-75 on Thursday night. Corey Allen had 19 points and seven rebounds for Georgia State (9-5, 3-4 Sun Belt Conference). Eliel Nsoseme added 14 points and 12 rebounds. Kane Williams had 13 points. Zack Bryant had 21 points for the Eagles (12-10, 6-7). Gedi Juozapaitis added 17 points. Eric Boone had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
